                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.711/13: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-02-19T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 19, 1929—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>69. Your 109, February 13, 7 p.m. Department would be interested to have any
                    further information concerning the matter and desires that you consult with Fox
                    with a view to making such representations as may seem wise and necessary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
